{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cd1483f705","title":"给诗刊的第二封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f88e7eb8ec","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":1,"articleId":"cd1483f705","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"acabb2a5c7","type":"title","text":"给诗刊的第二封信","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"cd1483f705","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ccc83efc95","type":"paragraph","text":"×××、××二位同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"cd1483f705","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b2fd15ca37","type":"paragraph","text":"信收到，近日写了两首七律，录上呈改。如以为可，可以上诗刊。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"cd1483f705","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c2b7b1f987","type":"paragraph","text":"近日右倾机会主义猖狂进攻，说人民事业这也不好，那也不好。全世界反华反共分子以及我国无产阶级内部、党的内部，过去混进来的资产阶级、小资产阶级的投机分子，他们里应外合，一起猖狂进攻。好家伙，简直要把昆仑山脉推下去了。同志，且慢！国内挂着共产主义招牌的一小撮投机分子，不过捡起几片鸡毛蒜皮，当作旗帜，向党的总路线、大跃进、人民公社举行攻击，真是“蚍蜉撼大树，可笑不自量”了。全世界反动派从去年起，咒骂我们狗血喷头。照我看，好得很。六亿五千万伟大人民的伟大事业而不被帝国主义及其在各国走狗大骂而特骂，那就是不可理解的了。他们越骂得凶，我就越高兴。让他们骂上半个世纪吧！那时再看，究竟谁败谁胜。我这两首诗，也算是答复那些忘八蛋的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"cd1483f705","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb90d1d77c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"cd1483f705","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5447b607a4","type":"subdate","text":"九月一日","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"cd1483f705","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6f5847445","type":"paragraph","text":"附两首律诗：","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"cd1483f705","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4cee8f2